'''Cragii''' was the written and spoken [[Language/Legends|language]] of the [[Cragmoloid/Legends|Cragmoloid]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Ankus/Legends|Ankus]].<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

Cragmoloids leaving their homeworld, and many Cragmoloid commoners who stayed there, used to learn [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]].<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

